        %p Like many other churches, we’ve had to make some changes during this season. Our church has not closed, but we are meeting in different ways!  We’re keeping this page as up to date as possible to help you stay resourced. If you are looking for Resources during this period to help you reflect or pray, please find below some things that we have referred to during our Sunday Livestream services, or that we think might be helpful.
        %h2 sundays
        %p 
          All our Sunday talks and worship sessions can be found on the Winchester Vineyard YouTube channel. These might help you to worship God or you can share them with friends. Although we can’t physically gather in our building, we are hosting a Sunday livestream, featuring worship and a talk - we'd love you to join us! You can tune in live every Sunday morning at 10:30 on our facebook page at 
          %a{:href => 'https://www.facebook.com/winchestervineyardchurch/'} facebook.com/winchestervineyardchurch
          where you will be able to comment and engage live. If you are not able to watch on facebook or you'd like to find out how to watch a previous livestream, head to
          %a{:href => 'http://www.winvin.org.uk/live/'} winvin.org.uk/live.
        %p  
          Sunday 29 March:
        %p
